<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.6">
<l>tampi yoṭutāmo ruvartantu ṇaivikātal tuṇaiyāka muṉanāḷ</l>
<l>vempi yerikāṉa kamulāvu mavartāmi ṉitumēvu nakartāṉ</l>
<l>kompu kutikoṇṭu kuyilkūva mayilālu meḻilārpu ṟavucēr</l>
<l>nampi yuṟaikiṉṟa nakarnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram, the city where the noble dwells</l>
<l>In the beautiful hill tracts where peacocks call, as coocoos coo,</l>
<l rend="indent">continually hopping on branches,</l>
<l>The city where lives [there] happily the one who had wandered long ago</l>
<l rend="indent">in the scorching hot forest</l>
<l>With a loving companionship between [his] younger brother, himself,</l>
<l rend="indent">and his wife.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
